      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i need to ask u something. i feel like im going crazy but i saw something today that i cant explain. i was looking at this specific cracked coffee mug in a shop window and it just... i don't know, it felt heavy, like it was \"stuck\" in a moment. then an hour later i saw on the news that there was a massive accident at a cafe downtown. it's like the mug was showing me what was gonna happen before it actually did. does that even make sense? or am i just losing it?",
